T1  - Determinants of conglomerate and predatory acquisitions: evidence from the 1960s
AU  - Barber, Brad M.
AU  - Palmer, Donald
AU  - Wallace, James
JO  - Journal of Corporate Finance
VL  - 1
IS  - 3
SP  - 283
EP  - 318
PY  - 1995
